>\n<section class=\"col-lg-offset-4 col-md-offset-4 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-4\" id=\"wb-srch\">\n<h2>Search</h2>\n<form action=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship/search.html\" method=\"get\" name=\"cse-search-box\" role=\"search\">\n<div class=\"form-group wb-srch-qry\">\n<label class=\"wb-inv\" for=\"wb-srch-q\">Search IRCC</label>\n<input class=\"wb-srch-q form-control\" id=\"wb-srch-q\" list=\"wb-srch-q-ac\" maxlength=\"170\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search IRCC\" size=\"34\" type=\"search\" value=\"\"/>\n<datalist id=\"wb-srch-q-ac\">\n</datalist>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group submit\">\n<button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-small\" id=\"wb-srch-sub\" name=\"wb-srch-sub\" type=\"submit\"><span class=\"glyphicon-search glyphicon\"></span><span class=\"wb-inv\">Search</span></button>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<nav class=\"gcweb-menu\" typeof=\"SiteNavigationElement\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Menu</h2>\n<button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Main </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-offset-6 col-xs-6 col-md-offset-0 col-md-4\">\n<section id=\"wb-so\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Sign in</h2>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/account.html\"><span class=\"visible-xs\">IRCC sign in</span><span class=\"hidden-xs\">IRCC sign in</span></a>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada.html\">Live in Canada</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures.html\">Ukraine immigration measures</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification.html\">Closed: Permanent residence for Ukrainian nationals with family members in Canada</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Closed: Permanent residence for Ukrainian nationals with family members in Canada</h1>\n<ul>\n<li> <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/eligibility.html\">Who can apply</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply.html\">How to apply</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/after-apply.html\">After you apply</a> </li>\n<li> <a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Apply for an open work permit, study permit or to extend your stay in Canada</a> </li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Apply for an open work permit, study permit or to extend your stay in Canada as a temporary resident</h1>\n<p>If you submitted or were included in an application for the permanent residence pathway for Ukrainian nationals with family members in Canada, you may be able to apply for</p>\n<ul>\n<li>an open work permit</li>\n<li>a study permit</li>\n<li>to stay in Canada longer as a temporary resident</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This new public policy will let you work, study or stay in Canada longer as a temporary resident while your permanent residence application is being processed.</p>\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld\" id=\"ff\">\n<form class=\"gc-font-2019\">\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n\t\t\t\"noForm\": true,\n\t\t\t\"isoptional\": false,\n\t\t\t\"renderas\":\"radio\",\n            \"gcChckbxrdio\": true,\n\t\t\t\"hideelm\": \".result\",\n\t\t\t\"base\": { \"live\": true, \"renderas\":\"radio\", \"gcChckbxrdio\": true },\n\t\t\t\"default\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\":\"#open, #study, #extend\"},\n            \"reset\": { \"action\" : \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#open, #study, #extend\"}\n\t\t\t}'>\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow-header\">\n<p class=\"wb-fieldflow-label\">What would you like to apply for?</p>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#open\"}'>Open work permit</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#study\"}'>Study permit</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#extend\"}'>Extend my stay as a visitor</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"open\">\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-0 h3\">Open work permit</h2>\n<p>Apply</p>\n<ul>\n<li>for a new open work permit</li>\n<li>to extend your open work permit, or</li>\n<li>to restore your status and apply for a work permit</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/open-work-permit.html\">Apply\n\t\t\t\tfor a work permit</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"study\">\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">New study permit</h3>\n<p>Apply for a new study permit under this public policy.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary mrgn-tp-md\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/study-permit.html\">Apply for a study permit</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Extend my study permit</h3>\n<p>Apply to extend your study permit through our regular application process if you currently hold a valid study\n\t\t\tpermit.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary mrgn-tp-md\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/extend-study-permit.html\">Extend your study permit</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Restore my status and apply for a study permit</h3>\n<p>If you lost your status <strong>less than</strong> 90 days ago, you may be able to apply to restore it and get a study permit through our regular application process.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary mrgn-tp-md\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/extend-study-permit/expired-permit.html\">Restore\n\t\t\t\tmy status</a></p>\n<details class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">\n<summary><strong>If you lost your status more than 90 days ago</strong></summary>\n<p>You may be eligible to restore your status and apply for a new study permit under this public policy if at the time we received the permanent residence application you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>had valid temporary resident status, or</li>\n<li>were out of status for less than 90 days</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"label label-danger\">Deadline</span> If your status expired more than 90 days ago, you must\n\t\t\t\tapply to restore it on or before <strong>March 31, 2026</strong>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/study-permit.html\">Apply\n\t\t\t\t\tfor a study permit under the public policy</a></p>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"extend\">\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Extend my stay as a visitor</h3>\n<p>Apply to extend your visitor status through our regular application process if you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>currently have valid temporary resident status</li>\n<li>are not applying for a work or study permit</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/extend-stay/apply.html\">Extend my stay</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Restore my status as a temporary resident</h3>\n<p>If you lost your temporary resident status <strong>less than</strong> 90 days ago, you may be eligible to apply to restore it through our regular application process.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary mrgn-tp-md\" href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1250&amp;top=16\">How to restore my status</a></p>\n<details class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">\n<summary><strong>If you lost your status more than 90 days ago</strong></summary>\n<p>You may be eligible to restore your status under this public policy if at the time we received the permanent residence application, you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>had valid temporary resident status, or</li>\n<li>were out of status for less than 90 days</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"label label-danger\">Deadline</span> If your status expired more than 90 days ago, you must apply to restore it on or before <strong>March 31, 2026</strong>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/restore.html\">Restore your status under the public policy</a></p>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<!--<h2>Sections</h2>\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"#a1\">Who can apply</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"#a2\">How to apply</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"#a3\">After you apply</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"#a4\">Optional: Apply for a work permit, study permit or to extend your stay in Canada</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you submitted, or were included, in an application for the permanent residence pathway for Ukrainian nationals with family members in Canada, under a new public policy, you may be able to apply for</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>an open work permit</li>\n\t<li>a study permit</li>\n\t<li>to stay in Canada longer as a temporary resident</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This will let you work, study or stay in Canada longer as a temporary resident while your permanent residence application is being processed.</p>\n\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld\" id=\"ff\">\n    <form class=\"gc-font-2019\">\n        <div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n\t\t\t\"noForm\": true,\n\t\t\t\"isoptional\": false,\n\t\t\t\"renderas\":\"radio\",\n            \"gcChckbxrdio\": true,\n\t\t\t\"hideelm\": \".result\",\n\t\t\t\"base\": { \"live\": true, \"renderas\":\"radio\", \"gcChckbxrdio\": true },\n\t\t\t\"default\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\":\"#open, #study, #extend\"},\n            \"reset\": { \"action\" : \"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#open, #study, #extend\"}\n\t\t\t}'>\n            <div class='wb-fieldflow-header'>\n                <p class='wb-fieldflow-label'>What would you like to apply for?</p>\n            </div>\n            <ul>\n                <li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#open\"}'>Open work permit</li>\n                <li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#study\"}'>Study permit</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\": \"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#extend\"}'>Extend my stay as a temporary resident</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </form>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"open\" class=\"result\">\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Open work permit</h3>\n\t\t<p>Apply</p>\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li>for a new open work permit</li>\n\t\t\t<li>to extend your open work permit, or</li>\n\t\t\t<li>to restore your status and apply for a work permit</li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\"\n\t\t\t\thref=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/open-work-permit.html\">Apply\n\t\t\t\tfor a work permit</a></p>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"study\" class=\"result\">\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">New study permit</h3>\n\t\t<p>Apply for a new study permit under this public policy.</p>\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\"\n\t\t\t\thref=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/study-permit.html\">Apply for a study permit</a>\n\t\t</p>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Extend my study permit</h3>\n\t\t<p>Apply to extend your study permit through our regular application process if you currently hold a valid study\n\t\t\tpermit.</p>\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\"\n\t\t\t\thref=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/extend-study-permit.html\">Extend your study permit</a>\n\t\t</p>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Restore my status and apply for a study permit</h3>\n\t\t<p>If you lost your status <strong>less than</strong> 90 days ago, you may be able to apply to restore it and get a\n\t\t\tnew study permit.</p>\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\"\n\t\t\t\thref=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/extend-study-permit/expired-permit.html\">Restore\n\t\t\t\tmy status</a></p>\n\t\t<details>\n\t\t\t<summary><strong>If you lost your status more than 90 days ago</strong></summary>\n\t\t\t<p>You may be eligible to restore your status and apply for a new study permit under this public policy if</p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>you had valid temporary resident status when the permanent residence application was received by us, or\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>you lost your temporary resident status no more than 90 days before you made the permanent residence\n\t\t\t\t\tapplication</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"label label-danger\">Deadline</span>&nbsp;If your status expired more than 90 days ago, you must\n\t\t\t\tapply to restore it on or before <strong>March 31, 2026</strong>.</p>\n\t\n\t\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\"\n\t\t\t\t\thref=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/study-permit.html\">Apply\n\t\t\t\t\tfor a study permit under the public policy</a></p>\n\t\t</details>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"extend\" class=\"result\">\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Extend my stay as a temporary resident</h3>\n\t\t<p>Apply to extend your temporary resident status through our regular application process if you</p>\n\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t<li>currently have valid temporary resident status</li>\n\t\t\t<li>are not applying for a work or study permit</li>\n\t\t</ul>\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/extend-stay/apply.html\">Extend my stay</a></p>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"well\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Restore my status as a temporary resident</h3>\n\t\t<p>If you lost your temporary resident status <strong>less than</strong> 90 days ago, you may be eligible to apply to restore it through our regular application process.</p>\n\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1250&top=16\">How to restore my status</a></p>\n\t\n\t\t<details>\n\t\t\t<summary><strong>If you lost your status more than 90 days ago</strong></summary>\n\t\t\t<p>You may be able to apply to restore your status under this public policy if</p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>you had valid temporary resident status when the permanent residence application was received by us, or</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>you lost your temporary resident status no more than 90 days before you made the permanent residence application</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"label label-danger\">Deadline</span>&nbsp;If your status expired more than 90 days ago, you must apply to restore it on or before <strong>March 31, 2026</strong>.</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/ukraine-measures/pr-family-reunification/apply-temporary-residence/restore.html\">Restore your status under the public policy</a></p>\n\t\t</details>\n\t</div>\n</div>-->\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2026-02-02\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/index-featured-can.asp\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc.html\">Contact us</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/ser